OL,7,FThe Commissioner of London's
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police Service, Sir Mark
OL,9,FRowley, has issued an apology to the
OL,10,Fcity's LGBT+ community for historical
OL,11,Fhomophobic persecution by the force.
OL,13,FHis apology came in response to a
OL,14,Fcampaign launched on Wednesday by
OL,15,FPeter Tatchell, which late TV star
OL,16,FPaul O'Grady was set to front before
OL,17,Fhis death. In a video for the
OL,18,Fcampaign, O'Grady had recalled 1980s
OL,19,Fpolice raids on gay bars during his
OL,20,Ftime performing as drag icon Lily
OL,21,FSavage.
OL,3,CMet Police chief issues apology for
OL,4,Chomophobic persecution after Paul
OL,5,CO'Grady-backed campaign
